Title: Alarm
Actors: Bamshad Abedi-Amin, Ciara Baxendale, Eliot Otis Brown Walters, Dan Cohen
Plot: Rae's still madly in love with Finn, but will her insecurities sabotage their relationship before it's even begun? Meanwhile, Kester encourages her to face her demons and finally confront the truth about what happened to Tix.
